# .Xcompose: changes compose so you don't get silly consonants with unreasonable diacritics
# run `ibus restart` to have it applied
# You also need to set up your input method to xim
# .Xmodmap: Changes AltGr behavior to get some czech characters like š and ů add `xmodmap path_to_.Xmodmap to your .profile
# https://askubuntu.com/questions/333897/how-to-apply-xmodmap-permanently
